        {
            "title": "龔嘉欣新劇易角否認離巢  視后放低身段「攪屎棍」通渠",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/fe1251753fe815ec153ec717f5abea91/2025-05/page_207.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/604f3121318071f0bfa187c6371c0102/c9f9fb7aba324ceeb2ff1b8d00d4ceaa-e916611f8b040034b011294338f19598-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-6825d60e3a109\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-6825d60e3a10b\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"龔嘉欣新劇易角否認離巢  視后放低身段「攪屎棍」通渠\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3d72a1f37b37309b4b0835b461253bc6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250515/_2025051519440451884.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">龔嘉欣新劇易角否認離巢  視后放低身段「攪屎棍」通渠</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>龔嘉欣、黎諾㦤、賴慰玲、劉穎鏇、吳偉豪到將軍澳電視城出席《一日打工限定》記者會，嘉欣在節目中體驗做「渠王」，她笑言是最有挑戰性的工作，節目組有問她的尺度，她有概念但沒想到要親手吸糞，幸好師傅「憐香惜玉」，都有體驗「攪屎棍」。\n\n</p><h2>龔嘉欣望大滿貫</h2>\n<p>嘉欣透露有女性入行，雖然人工高福利好，亦有厭惡性，她會尊重，問到想做甚麼工作？她表示想做馬伕照顧馬匹。嘉欣早前在社交網更改聯絡方式，被指即將離巢，問是否因離巢才被安排做「渠王」？她否認，又指視后獎座近日才刻好名放在家中，澄清目前仍是TVB經理人約。至於被指有份參演《璀璨之城》，之後卻易角，她指沒留意到是否有特別安排，表示已和該劇監製合作多次，每次角色都有挑戰性，期待下一次合作。嘉欣指最近忙拍綜藝節目和廣告，公司知道她尚欠「最佳女主持」才大滿貫，得獎後已拍了6個廣告，感謝獎項帶來機會。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250297/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"龔嘉欣、黎諾㦤、賴慰玲、劉穎鏇、吳偉豪在將軍澳電視城出席《一日打工限定》記者會。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/009e0aea403df484cee01eaaa025ffdd/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_16_04_53_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        龔嘉欣、黎諾㦤、賴慰玲、劉穎鏇、吳偉豪在將軍澳電視城出席《一日打工限定》記者會。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250595/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"龔嘉欣在節目中體驗「攪屎棍」工序。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b48b6a1b43f7cce4eea93c613e116d16/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_16_04_56_0.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        龔嘉欣在節目中體驗「攪屎棍」工序。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250304/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"劉穎鏇於《一日打工限定》中體驗飛機維修員工作。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/26aacbb0a0f05ea4d8dc076a35a16f9a/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_16_04_49_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        劉穎鏇於《一日打工限定》中體驗飛機維修員工作。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\