tributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        呢位飛機維修員好好身材。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250318/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"龔嘉欣指視后獎座近日才刻好名放在家中，澄清目前TVB仍是經理人。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/0af7d5ebd0361753da719ebe19b67bfd/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_16_04_55.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        龔嘉欣指視后獎座近日才刻好名放在家中，澄清目前TVB仍是經理人。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250321/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"龔嘉欣有份演《璀璨之城》，之後卻易角，她指沒留意到是否有特別安排，表示期待下次與該劇監製陳維冠合作。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cd0b39975921f4dcd67f225a95624413/2025-05/WhatsApp_Image_2025-05-15_at_16_04_57_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        龔嘉欣有份演《璀璨之城》，之後卻易角，她指沒留意到是否有特別安排，表示期待下次與該劇監製陳維冠合作。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4250648/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"《璀璨之城》是豪門恩怨劇，主演包括吳卓羲、 張智霖、林夏薇、石修等。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2045f69908ff8aff6831a51b1c01da76/2025-05/672ca35264d98_1730978642_10668492306776ca7a90d01-1024x1024.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        《璀璨之城》是豪門恩怨劇，主演包括吳卓羲、 張智霖、林夏薇、石修等。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
